 for MEWS, 1 (IQR, 0-39) hour for EDI, and 0 (IQR, 0-42) hours for RI. CONCLUSIONS AND RELEVANCE In this cohort study of inpatient encounters, eCART outperformed the other AI and non-AI scores, identifying more deteriorating patients with fewer false alarms and sufficient time to intervene. NEWS, a non-AI, publicly available early warning score, significantly outperformed EDI. Given the wide variation in accuracy, additional transparency and oversight of early warning tools may be warranted.},
